Kopimi! I encourage copying that denies all consideration of copyright and similar bullshit [1]
[as per the (un)liscense this code is explicitly dedicated to the public domain]

--- to install ---
1. Move the noClipboardButton@marius.albrecht.freenet.de directory into
    ~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extenstions/
2. Restart your gnome shell [how depends on your desktop, just look it up]
3. Enable the extension by using the gnome extensions app or the 
    gnome-extensions cli tool

[1] https://kopimi.com/kopimi/ #A-Famous-Quotation-as-a-Kopimist-Creed